headline: Bunge to Provide Business Update Oct. 15
summary: ST. LOUIS, September 29, 2025--Bunge Global SA (NYSE: BG) will provide a business update on Wednesday, Oct. 15, prior to the market opening.

headline: Diana Shipping Inc. Announces Time Charter Contract for m/v DSI Aquila with Bunge
summary: ATHENS, Greece, Sept. 29, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Diana Shipping Inc. (NYSE: DSX), (the “Company”), a global shipping company specializing in the ownership and bareboat charter-in of dry bulk vessels, today announced that through a separate wholly-owned subsidiary, it has entered into a time charter contract with Bunge SA, Geneva, for one of its Ultramax dry bulk vessels, the m/v DSI Aquila.
